                    <comment id="13145283" author="c_koell" created="Mon, 7 Nov 2011 08:12:45 +0000"  >I would prefer that if we use the &amp;quot;old&amp;quot; parameters homeDir and configFile to create the repository not transient (create repo via RepositoryConfig.create)&lt;br/&gt;
