                    <comment id="13167432" author="c_koell" created="Mon, 12 Dec 2011 09:38:42 +0000"  >Thanks for hint i opened a new issue &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-3176&quot; title=&quot;JCARepositoryManager does not close InputStream&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JCR-3176&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</comment>
                    <comment id="13174914" author="orair" created="Thu, 22 Dec 2011 17:31:35 +0000"  >There is another problem with this patch.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
If config is null, it will call the method in line 108:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;config = RepositoryConfig.create(configFile, homeDir);&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
